subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: After speculation that she would defect to the more lucrative Nascar Nextel Cup, Danica Patrick will remain with the I.R.L. but move to Andretti Green Racing.
snippet: After speculation that she would defect to the more lucrative Nascar Nextel Cup, Danica Patrick will remain with the I.R.L. but move to Andretti Green Racing.
